{"text_id":185868,"tokens":["In"," recent"," years",","," there"," has"," been"," a"," growing"," trend"," of"," parents"," choosing"," to"," have"," their"," children"," take"," classes"," from"," the"," comfort"," of"," their"," own"," homes","."," This"," shift"," from"," traditional"," classroom"," learning"," to"," home","-","based"," education"," has"," been"," driven"," by"," a"," variety"," of"," factors",","," including"," the"," desire"," for"," greater"," flexibility",","," concerns"," about"," the"," quality"," of"," education"," in"," traditional"," schools",","," and"," the"," need"," for"," a"," safer"," learning"," environment","."," Whatever"," the"," reasons"," may"," be",","," it"," is"," clear"," that"," home","-","based"," education"," offers"," a"," number"," of"," significant"," benefits"," for"," students",","," including"," greater"," academic"," flexibility",","," a"," more"," personalized"," learning"," experience",","," and"," increased"," safety"," and"," security",".","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," primary"," reasons"," why"," parents"," choose"," to"," have"," their"," children"," take"," classes"," from"," home"," is"," the"," desire"," for"," greater"," flexibility","."," In"," traditional"," classroom"," settings",","," the"," pace"," of"," learning"," is"," often"," dictated"," by"," the"," curriculum"," and"," the"," needs"," of"," the"," group"," as"," a"," whole","."," This"," can"," be"," frustrating"," for"," students"," who"," may"," need"," more"," time"," to"," grasp"," certain"," concepts",","," as"," well"," as"," for"," those"," who"," are"," ready"," to"," move"," ahead"," at"," a"," faster"," pace",".","\n\n","At"," home",","," on"," the"," other"," hand",","," students"," have"," the"," freedom"," to"," learn"," at"," their"," own"," pace",","," taking"," the"," time"," they"," need"," to"," fully"," understand"," new"," concepts"," before"," moving"," on"," to"," the"," next"," lesson","."," This"," can"," help"," to"," reduce"," stress"," and"," anxiety",","," as"," students"," are"," not"," constantly"," feeling"," pressured"," to"," keep"," up"," with"," their"," peers","."," Additionally",","," home","-","based"," education"," allows"," for"," a"," more"," personalized"," learning"," experience",","," as"," parents"," and"," teachers"," can"," tailor"," the"," curriculum"," to"," meet"," the"," unique"," needs"," and"," interests"," of"," each"," individual"," student",".","\n\n","Another"," significant"," benefit"," of"," home","-","based"," education"," is"," the"," increased"," safety"," and"," security"," it"," provides","."," In"," today","'","s"," world",","," concerns"," about"," school"," violence"," and"," bullying"," are"," at"," an"," all","-","time"," high","."," By"," learning"," from"," home",","," students"," are"," able"," to"," avoid"," many"," of"," the"," risks"," and"," dangers"," associated"," with"," traditional"," schools","."," Additionally",","," home","-","based"," education"," allows"," parents"," to"," have"," a"," greater"," level"," of"," control"," over"," their"," children","'","s"," social"," interactions",","," enabling"," them"," to"," carefully"," screen"," and"," monitor"," the"," people"," their"," children"," interact"," with",".","\n\n","In"," addition"," to"," these"," benefits",","," home","-","based"," education"," has"," also"," been"," shown"," to"," have"," a"," positive"," impact"," on"," academic"," performance","."," According"," to"," a"," study"," conducted"," by"," the"," National"," Home"," Education"," Research"," Institute",","," the"," average"," home","-","educated"," student"," performs"," at"," the"," ","8","6","th"," percentile"," on"," standardized"," academic"," achievement"," tests",","," compared"," to"," the"," national"," average"," of"," the"," ","5","0","th"," percentile","."," This"," suggests"," that"," home","-","based"," education"," may"," be"," a"," more"," effective"," way"," of"," teaching"," students",","," as"," it"," allows"," for"," a"," more"," personalized"," and"," flexible"," learning"," experience",".","\n\n","However",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," note"," that"," home","-","based"," education"," is"," not"," without"," its"," challenges","."," One"," of"," the"," primary"," challenges"," faced"," by"," parents"," who"," choose"," to"," educate"," their"," children"," at"," home"," is"," the"," need"," to"," balance"," the"," demands"," of"," teaching"," with"," the"," needs"," of"," the"," family","."," This"," can"," be"," particularly"," challenging"," for"," parents"," who"," work"," full","-","time"," jobs"," or"," who"," have"," multiple"," children"," to"," care"," for",".","\n\n","Another"," challenge"," faced"," by"," home","-","educated"," students"," is"," the"," lack"," of"," social"," interaction"," and"," extracurricular"," activities","."," While"," home","-","based"," education"," does"," provide"," a"," safe"," and"," secure"," learning"," environment",","," it"," can"," also"," be"," isolating"," for"," students"," who"," are"," not"," able"," to"," participate"," in"," the"," same"," types"," of"," activities"," and"," social"," events"," as"," their"," peers"," in"," traditional"," schools",".","\n\n","Despite"," these"," challenges",","," it"," is"," clear"," that"," home","-","based"," education"," offers"," a"," number"," of"," significant"," benefits"," for"," students","."," By"," providing"," a"," more"," personalized"," and"," flexible"," learning"," experience",","," as"," well"," as"," a"," safer"," and"," more"," secure"," environment",","," home","-","based"," education"," can"," help"," students"," to"," achieve"," academic"," success"," and"," reach"," their"," full"," potential",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," the"," trend"," towards"," home","-","based"," education"," is"," one"," that"," is"," likely"," to"," continue"," in"," the"," coming"," years","."," As"," more"," and"," more"," parents"," become"," aware"," of"," the"," benefits"," of"," this"," type"," of"," learning",","," it"," is"," likely"," that"," even"," more"," will"," choose"," to"," have"," their"," children"," take"," classes"," from"," home","."," Whether"," driven"," by"," the"," desire"," for"," greater"," flexibility",","," concerns"," about"," the"," quality"," of"," education"," in"," traditional"," schools",","," or"," the"," need"," for"," a"," safer"," learning"," environment",","," home","-","based"," education"," offers"," a"," number"," of"," significant"," benefits"," for"," students",","," including"," greater"," academic"," flexibility",","," a"," more"," personalized"," learning"," experience",","," and"," increased"," safety"," and"," security","."," While"," it"," is"," not"," without"," its"," challenges",","," home","-","based"," education"," is"," a"," trend"," that"," is"," likely"," to"," continue"," to"," grow"," and"," thrive"," in"," the"," coming"," years","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}